platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Rec Room is a sprawling, vibrant universe of wildly different multiplayer experiences, which makes it easy to find whatever were in the mood for. We can play paintball, slay monsters in dungeons, or simply hang out with friends on a moonlit island beachand so much more. But its not all about playing: Rec Room lets us make things too. With intuitive tools for creating and sharing our own experiences, Rec Room provides a fantastic way to turn imagination into digital reality.
